    <para id="import-auto-id1164847841104">Equation 4 indicates that at low frequency the magnitude of the transfer function increases at +20dB per decade as shown in Figure 1.b.</para>
    <para id="import-auto-id1164847880876">
      <emphasis effect="bold">Figure 1.(i) Magnitude of the transfer function in dB(decibels) vs Frequency(logarithmic scale) of High Pass Filter(HPF)</emphasis>
    </para>
    <para id="import-auto-id1164855397526">
      <emphasis effect="bold">(ii) Phase of the transfer function in dB(decibels) vs Frequency(logarithmic scale)of HPF.</emphasis>
    </para>
    <para id="import-auto-id1164846515543">
