    <para id="import-auto-id1164847869584">
      <emphasis effect="bold">Figure 2. The Time domain response of High Pass Filter for three cases: (i) When T &lt;&lt; τ  (ii) When  T &gt;&gt; τ and (iii) when T  ≈ τ .</emphasis>
    </para>
    <para id="import-auto-id1164847744960">From the 10% sag frequency the lower cut-off frequency can be directly calculated.</para>
    <para id="import-auto-id1164847261022">Suppose the 10% sag frequency is f* then we have the following formulation:</para>
